“Oh, very severe!” chimed in the patient himself; then suddenly altering 
his voice, “Drinking hot rum toddies with me every night, till he couldn’t 
see to put on the bandages; and sending me to bed, half seas over, about three 
o’clock in the morning. Oh, ye stars! he sat up with me indeed, and was very 
severe in my diet. Oh! a great watcher, and very dietetically severe, is Dr. 
